                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    Mainly in northern Taiwan, at altitudes of 500-1000 m. Endangered. <a class="site-link" href="http://archive.zo.ntu.edu.tw/rept_map.asp?rept_id=R0072">(Distribution map).</a>
                </div>
